### 变量定义 (可根据实际部署修改)
@host = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

### 1. 健康检查 (Health Check)
# 验证服务是否启动
GET {{host}}/api/health-check-http
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

### 2. 用户注册 (Register Email) - 成功场景
# 测试正常的注册流程
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register-email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "张三",
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### 3. 用户注册 (Register Email) - 重复邮箱测试
# 运行完上面的请求后，再次运行此请求应返回 409 Conflict
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register-email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "张三副本",
  "email": "zhangsan@example.com",
  "password": "AnotherPassword123!"
}

### 4. 用户注册 (Register Email) - 参数缺失测试
# 测试缺少必填字段，应返回 400 Bad Request
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register-email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "李四",
  "email": "" 
}

### 5. 用户注册 (Register Email) - JSON 格式错误测试
# 测试无效的 JSON 结构，应返回 400 Bad Request
POST {{host}}/api/auth/register-email
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "王五",
  "email": "wangwu@example.com"
  "password": "MissingComma" 
}